        <item>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Fairness to Pet Owners Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>Directs the Federal Trade Commission to require prescribers of animal drugs to verify prescriptions and provide copies of prescriptions to pet owners, pet owner designees, and pharmacies, without the prescriber demanding payment or establishing other conditions. </p>Treats a violation of this Act as an unfair or deceptive act or practice under the Federal Trade Commission Act.]]></text>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2015-06-05T21:07:02Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <actionDate>2015-05-06</actionDate>
          <updateDate>2015-05-06T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
        </item>
